  Nigerian singer, Perruzzi has been trending on Twitter NG for all the wrong reasons. We earlier reported how he allegedly assaulted social media influencer, Adegoke Pamilerin and how Nigerians reacted to the issue. Now, Davido has tweeted an apology to Pamilerin on behalf of Perruzzi, in the heat of the moment. Rumour has it that Pamilerin was given a hundred thousand naira as compensation but until that’s confirmed, let’s hope the ‘Assurance’ crooner’s tweets helps ease the tension. Read his tweet below:  Meanwhile, earlier in the day, Nigeria Police ACP, Yomi Shogunle took to his twitter account to indirectly address the issue, revealing how much Pamilerin can make from the infamous dirty slap he received from Perruzzi.  In case you missed it, read reactions to the trending issue here. 